reviewText: Received my movies yesterday and everything was actually what they said. Thank you
I love this DVD set because it has both Season 5 (Imperfect Cell and Perfect Cell Sagas) and Season 6 (Cell Games Saga).
This product was really good. I would recommend it because it was well worth the money. It came in perfect condition.
Arrived just as expected. Worth the purchase. Great!!!  To all true dragon ball z fans this purchase will satisfy your needs. I love it.
